This folder contains more complex, public domain, (or in countries where
that is not applicable, BSD-3) examples of use, and is referenced both in the
doc/ documentation and on the wiki.

Current examples:
miniwm/
minimalistic window manager supporting external
connections and adopting crashed sessions.

histoview/
showing how calctargets can be used to dynamically
generate histograms.

shmif-conn/
skeleton code (with build system) for performing non-authoritative connections,
polling event-queue and drawing a solid color surface.
